::Battera::

She landed near CyberShark.  She looked about and saw no one.  She crossd 
her wings around her.  She felt a cold chill run down her back.  She didn't 
like this.  She looked around and called out, "Hello, it's me, Battera. 
Vulios? Are you here? Are you OK?"
She looked about and saw no one, not Vulios or anyone.
She looked at the ground. She didn't like this.  She had a sinking feeling 
in her spark.
"I don't think he's going to show right now.  He won't want to see me 
anyways."
She looked at CyberShark. "Let's go. I have the feeling I'm not welcome 
here."
She spread her wings and headed skyward.
